ed="T" n="0886a11"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0886a11"/><head><date from-iso="+0960-02-09" key="j20717322132856" to-iso="+1127-06-18"><anchor xml:id="beg0886001"/>宋<anchor xml:id="end0886001"/></date><placeName key="PL000000057754">東京觀音禪院</placeName><persName key="A013791">巖俊</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0886a12"/><persName key="A013791">釋巖俊</persName>，姓<name>廉氏</name>，<placeName key="PL000000001808">邢臺</placeName>人也。誕育之來，蔚繁神<lb
ed="T" n="0886a13"/>異，挺身去縛，誓入空門。從捧戒珠，終身圓<lb
ed="T" n="0886a14"/>瑩。乃持杯錫，言遍參尋，陟彼<placeName key="PL000000028928">衡</placeName><placeName key="PL000000018775">廬</placeName>，登乎<placeName key="PL000000034802">岷<lb
ed="T" n="0886a15"/>蜀</placeName>。嘗至<placeName key="PL000000027093">鳳林</placeName><ptr target="#n3459"/>，欻逢深谷，見一區之晃耀，原<lb
ed="T" n="0886a16"/>七寶之縱橫。時同侶相顧曰：「奇哉！可俯拾乎？」<lb
ed="T" n="0886a17"/><persName key="A013791">俊</persName>曰：「古人鋤園，觸黃金若瓦礫耳<ptr target="#n3460"/>。苟欲懷<lb
ed="T" n="0886a18"/>之，自速禍也。徯<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2295"/>吾野菅覆頂<!-- 有棲身之所 -->，須此供四方<lb
ed="T" n="0886a19"/>僧。」言訖捨去，造謁<placeName key="PL000000015565"><placeName>舒州</placeName><placeName>投子山</placeName></placeName><ref type="person" target="#A009447">主</ref>，問<ref type="person" target="#A013791">之</ref>曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0886a20"/>「<ref type="person" target="#A013791">客</ref>來昨宿何處？」<persName key="A013791">俊</persName>曰：「在不動道場。<ptr target="#n3461"/>」曰：「既言<lb
ed="T" n="0886a21"/>不動，曷由至此？」對曰：「至此豈是動<anchor xml:id="beg0886002"/>耶<anchor xml:id="end0886002"/>？」曰：「元<lb
ed="T" n="0886a22"/>來宿不著處<ptr target="#n3468"/>。」然<ref type="person" target="#A009447">山主</ref>默認許<ref type="person" target="#A013791">之</ref>。迨思還<placeName key="PL000000001047">趙</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0886a23"/>路出<placeName key="PL000000023452">陳留</placeName>，抵今<placeName key="PL000000023467">東京</placeName>。屬乎<placeName key="PL000000048181">梁</placeName>少保<persName key="A013799"><persName>隴西公</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0886a24"/><persName>資</persName></persName>──即<placeName key="PL000000024712">河陽</placeName>節度使贈中書令<persName key="A013800">芝</persName>之昆也<ptr target="#n3462"/>──，雖居<lb
ed="T" n="0886a25"/>貴仕，酷信空門，接<persName key="A013791">俊</persName>談玄，若<persName key="A002809">劉遺民</persName>之奉<lb
ed="T" n="0886a26"/><persName key="A001204">賈遠</persName>也<ptr target="#n3463"/>。相與議捨第宅<ptr target="#n3465"/>俾建仁祠<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1894"/>。<persName key="A013791">俊</persName>弗讓<lb
ed="T" n="0886a27"/>違<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2296"/>，以安形性<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2297"/>。既考禪室<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2155"/>而行祖風，慕道窮<lb
ed="T" n="0886a28"/>玄，堂宇盈塞。<persName key="A006584">周高祖</persName>、<persName key="A006586">世宗</persName>二帝潛隱地<ptr target="#n3464"/>，與<persName key="A013791">俊</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0886a29"/>布衣之交，每登方丈<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2298"/>，必施跪禮。及其即位，<pb ed="T" n="0886b" xml:id="T50.2061.0886b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0886b01"/>延遲<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2299"/>優渥，至乎朝達，見必稽顙<ptr type="glossary" target="#g903"/>，高談虛論，若<lb
ed="T" n="0886b02"/>至寶山焉。以<date from-iso="+0966-03-30" key="j20739732074002" to-iso="+0966-04-28"><name>乾德</name>丙寅三月</date>示身有疾，<lb
ed="T" n="0886b03"/>彌留<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2301"/>，弟子求醫奉藥，<anchor xml:id="beg0886sgsz4"/><choice resp="PC-JK-MB"><sic>瞋</sic><corr>瞑</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0886sgsz4"/><ptr target="#n3431"/>目噤脣不食，垂<lb
ed="T" n="0886b04"/>誡門人後已，當怡顏儼肅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2300"/>，合掌訣眾而滅。享<lb
ed="T" n="0886b05"/>齡八十五，坐夏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g61"/>六十五。初<persName key="A013791">俊</persName>被朝恩，賜紫<lb
ed="T" n="0886b06"/>袈裟也，受而不服；錫<persName key="A013791">淨戒師</persName>號也<ptr target="#n3466"/>，有而不<lb
ed="T" n="0886b07"/>稱。屬其策杖清羸<ptr target="#n3467"/>，<persName key="A006584">周祖</persName>勅侍者輩勿令大<lb
ed="T" n="0886b08"/>師一中食，俾其日昃更進佉闍尼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2302"/>矣。<persName key="A013791">俊</persName>諾<lb
ed="T" n="0886b09"/>而難遵。慈柔被物，暨乎自狹而廣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2303"/>，實三院<lb
ed="T" n="0886b10"/>一門也──二堂東西，恒不減數百眾。五十年<anchor xml:id="beg0886sgsz5"/>間<anchor xml:id="end0886sgsz5"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0886b11"/>計供僧萬百千數。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023467">京城</ref>禪林，居其甲矣。以<lb
ed="T" n="0886b12"/><date key="j20740102074010" when-iso="+0966-05-06">其年四月八日</date>歸葬于東郊<placeName key="PL000000049325">豐臺村</placeName>，白塔存<lb
ed="T" n="0886b13"/>焉。于日神都<ptr target="#n2049"/>寺院各率幡幢，吹貝鳴鐃，相<lb
ed="T" n="0886b14"/>繼二三里。道俗送殯者萬數。知制誥<persName key="A013802">王著</persName>為<lb
ed="T" n="0886b15"/>碑昭懋厥德云。</p>
